<%- include('header', { title: 'Electronics Engineering Technology — Dawson College' }) %>

<main>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-grid"></div>
    <div class="hero-glow"></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-tag">DEC — 243.C0</div>
      <h1>Build the systems<br />that power <em>everything.</em></h1>
      <p class="hero-lead">
        The Electronics Engineering Technology program at Dawson College trains technicians to design,
        test, and troubleshoot the electronic systems at the core of modern industry.
      </p>
      <div class="btn-row">
        <a href="/program" class="btn btn-primary">Explore the Program</a>
        <a href="/courses" class="btn btn-outline">View Courses</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="stat-bar">
    <div class="stat-item">
      <span class="stat-number">3</span>
      <span class="stat-label">Year DEC Program</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-item">
      <span class="stat-number">6</span>
      <span class="stat-label">Semesters</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-item">
      <span class="stat-number">~30</span>
      <span class="stat-label">Lab Hours / Week</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-item">
      <span class="stat-number">95%</span>
      <span class="stat-label">Employment Rate</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-tag">What you'll learn</div>
    <h2>Core Areas of Study</h2>
    <p class="section-lead">
      From analog circuits to embedded programming, the program covers the full stack of modern electronics engineering technology.
    </p>

    <div class="card-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <span class="card-icon">⚡</span>
        <h3>Analog &amp; Digital Circuits</h3>
        <p>Analyze and design circuits using op-amps, transistors, logic gates, and signal conditioning components.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <span class="card-icon">🔌</span>
        <h3>Embedded Systems</h3>
        <p>Program microcontrollers in C and assembly to interface with sensors, actuators, and communication buses.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <span class="card-icon">📡</span>
        <h3>Telecommunications</h3>
        <p>Study modulation, signal propagation, and the fundamentals of wired and wireless communications.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <span class="card-icon">🏭</span>
        <h3>Industrial Automation</h3>
        <p>Configure PLCs, drive systems, and industrial sensors in simulated manufacturing environments.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <span class="card-icon">🛠️</span>
        <h3>PCB Design &amp; Fabrication</h3>
        <p>Design and prototype printed circuit boards using industry-standard EDA software and soldering techniques.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <span class="card-icon">📊</span>
        <h3>Test &amp; Measurement</h3>
        <p>Use oscilloscopes, spectrum analyzers, and multimeters to diagnose and validate electronic systems.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>

<%- include('footer') %>
